title: truesight
tooltip: see in darkness, see invisible things, see through illusions, and perceive the original form of shapechangers
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A creature with truesight can, out to a specific range, see in normal and magical darkness, see invisible creatures and objects, automatically detect visual illusions, and perceives the original form of a [[shapechanger]] or a creature that is transformed by magic. They can also see into the [[Ethereal Veil]].